>Multiple storage</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> destinations for extra safety</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Detailed reports of your backups</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Password protection for your UpdraftPlus backups to keep other administrators out</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/automatic-backups/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Automatic backups</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> before updating WordPress core, themes and plugins</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Install UpdraftPlus today and backup your site, safe in the knowledge that should the worst happen, you can restore your site in just a few minutes.</span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/how-to-backup-your-wordpress-site-in-one-minute/\">How to backup your WordPress site in one minute</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://updraftplus.com/how-to-backup-your-wordpress-site-in-one-minute/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n				